## Critical: Working Directory

When running Node.js scripts or npm commands, ALWAYS use `/Users/tanvir/career-ops/` as the working directory:

```bash
cd /Users/tanvir/career-ops/ && npm run doctor
cd /Users/tanvir/career-ops/ && node generate-pdf.mjs
cd /Users/tanvir/career-ops/ && npm run merge
```

All data files (CV, profile, applications tracker) are stored in `/Users/tanvir/career-ops/` and its subdirectories.